		<div class="section_timesquare _PM_timesquare_base" data-code="weather" data-monitor-weather="20191105104831">
<h2 class="blind">타임스퀘어</h2>
<div class="area_header">
<div class="header_info _PM_timesquare_info">
<a href="https://calendar.naver.com" data-clk="squ.date" class="hi_date"><span class="hi_dnum">11.05.</span><span class="hi_day">(화)</span></a><i class="hi_slash" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation">|</i>

<a href="#" data-clk="squ_wea.set" class="hi_tit _PM_timesquare_weather_loc">서울시 역삼동<i class="ico_btn_arrow" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
</div>
<div class="header_paging _PM_timesquare_navi">
</div>

    }

	var da_dom_id = 'p_main_job_00'.trim();

	var tarEl = NBP_CORP.$(uId);
	
	var util = naver_corp_da.Util ? new naver_corp_da.Util() : new NBP_CORP.Nimp();

	if(tarEl) {
		/* ActiveView */
		var ac_end_date = "20301231235959";
		var ad_end_date = "20301231235959";

		var orientation_change_time = 500;

		var callback = function () {
			var url = "https://nv.veta.naver.com/fxview?eu=EU10016020&calp=-&oj=MHdRRNq%2Fj%2FO0crxudfMwVI9mW%2FikRJ6VBazN69ObGo3AZJiIZoBgNfNDDNVi2S2v%2FTlSjVP0M%2FbL%2BOI%2FLWYrI3shs34rWx19oRfPfaro6VxIieaj%2FWa%2FYNl5oIOScG3I&ac=7560751&src=3184385&evtcd=V900&x_ti=944&tb=JOB_1&oid=&sid1=&sid2=&rk=d8c640b8df1d2f2555ec5167fc14e752&eltts=vh1ZLP9UPMb%2FYUZwXtZdrw%3D%3D&brs=Y&&eid=V900&x_ev=";

				x_ev = (target) ? ((parseInt(target.getBoundingClientRect().height || target.offsetHeight, 10) === 0) ? '000' : '111') : '000';

		};

		naver_corp_da.activeViews[uId] = new naver_corp_da.ActiveView({
